uve\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Qu\u00e9bec Cin\u00e9ma Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]] \n| Lubna Azabal\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[M\u00e9lissa D\u00e9sormeaux-Poulin]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Art Direction\n| Andr\u00e9-Line Beauparlant\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Cinematography\n| Andr\u00e9 Turpin\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Editing\n| Monique Dartonne\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Sound\n| Sylvain Bellemare, Jean Umansky and Jean-Pierre Laforce \n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Costume Design\n| Sophie Lefebvre \n| {{won}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[Lumi\u00e8res Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[17th Lumi\u00e8res Awards|13 January 2012]]\n| [[Lumi\u00e8res Award for Best French-Language Film|Best French-Language Film]]\n| Denis Villeneuve\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/the-artist-lumiere-awards-281420|title='The Artist' Named Best Film at France's Lumiere Awards|accessdate=8 August 2016|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924203654/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/the-artist-lumiere-awards-281420|archive-date=24 September 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[Magritte Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[2nd Magritte Awards|4 February 2012]]\n| [[Magritte Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| Lubna Azabal\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" |<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.journaldemontreal.com/2012/02/05/incendies-recompense-aux-magritte |title=Incendies r\u00e9compens\u00e9 aux Magritte |last=Demers |first=Maxime |date=5 February 2012 |accessdate=6 August 2016 |work=[[Le Journal de Montr\u00e9al]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006085101/http://www.journaldemontreal.com/2012/02/05/incendies-recompense-aux-magritte |archive-date=6 October 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[New York Film Critics Circle]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[2011 New York Film Critics Circle Awards|9 January 2012]]\n| [[New York Film Critics Circle Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]]\n| rowspan=\"8\" | Denis Villeneuve\n| {{draw|Runner-up}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" |<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2011/11/29/new-york-film-critics-cant-wait-to-give-its-top-prizes-to-the-artist/ |title=New York Film Critics Can\u2019t Wait to Give Their Top Prizes to The Artist |last=[[Richard Corliss|Corliss, Richard]] |first= |date=29 November 2011 |accessdate=7 August 2016 |work=[[Time (magazine)|Time]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814235030/http://entertainment.time.com/2011/11/29/new-york-film-critics-cant-wait-to-give-its-top-prizes-to-the-artist/ |archive-date=14 August 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[Toronto Film Critics Association]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[Toronto Film Critics Association Awards 2010|14 December 2010]]\n| [[Rogers Best Canadian Film Award|Best Canadian Film]]\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" |<ref>\n{{cite web|title=''Incendies'' wins the 2010 Rogers Best Canadian Film Award |publisher=Toronto Film Critics' Association |date=12 January 2011 |url=http://torontofilmcritics.com/blog/?p=52 |accessdate=19 September 2011 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110121112821/http://torontofilmcritics.com/blog/?p=52 |archivedate=21 January 2011 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[Toronto International Film Festival]]\n| rowspan=\"1\" | [[2010 Toronto International Film Festival|September 2010]]\n| [[Toronto International Film Festival Award for Best Canadian Film|Best Canadian Feature Film]]\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" |<ref name=\"Telefilm\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=3| [[Valladolid International Film Festival]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" | November 2010\n| Audience Award\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" | <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.actualites.uqam.ca/2010/film-incendies-denis-villeneuve-remporte-trois-prix-semaine-cinema-international-valladolid |title=Le film Incendies de Denis Villeneuve remporte trois prix \u00e0 la Semaine du cin\u00e9ma international de Valladolid |date=11 November 2010 |accessdate=31 March 2018 |publisher=[[Universit\u00e9 du Qu\u00e9bec \u00e0 Montr\u00e9al]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180331174745/https://www.actualites.uqam.ca/2010/film-incendies-denis-villeneuve-remporte-trois-prix-semaine-cinema-international-valladolid |archive-date=31 March 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Screenplay\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Youth Jury Award\n| {{won}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=5| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle]]\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 2011\n| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle Award for Best Canadian Film|Best Canadian Film]]\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"5\" |<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2011/01/social-network-incendies-leads-vancouver-critics-awards-243944/ |title='Social Network,' 'Incendies' Leads Vancouver Critics\u2019 Awards |last=Knegt |first=Peter |date=11 January 2011 |accessdate=6 August 2016 |work=[[IndieWire]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818101509/http://www.indiewire.com/2011/01/social-network-incendies-leads-vancouver-critics-awards-243944/ |archive-date=18 August 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle Award for Best Director of a Canadian Film|Best Director of a Canadian Film]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle Award for Best Actress in a Canadian Film|Best Actress in a Canadian Film]] \n| Lubna Azabal\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle Award for Best Supporting Actor in a Canadian Film|Best Supporting Actor in a Canadian Film]]\n| [[Maxim Gaudette]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Vancouver Film Critics Circle Award for Best Supporting Actress in a Canadian Film|Best Supporting Actress in a Canadian Film]]\n| M\u00e9lissa D\u00e9sormeaux-Poulin\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | [[Vancouver International Film Festival]]\n| 2011\n| Best Canadian Feature Film \n| Denis Villeneuve\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" |<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/incendies-best-canadian-film-toronto-critics-1.1072930 |title=Incendies best Canadian film: Toronto critics |last= |first= |date=12 January 2011 |accessdate=6 August 2016 |work=[[CBC News]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319072536/http://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/incendies-best-canadian-film-toronto-critics-1.1072930 |archive-date=19 March 2017 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of submissions to the 83rd Academy Awards for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n* [[List of Canadian submissions for the Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://www.trinityfilm.co.uk/films/incendies/|name=Official UK website}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.incendiesfilm.com/|name=Official U.S. website}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.incendies-thefilm.com/|name=Official Canadian website}} {{in lang|en}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.incendies-lefilm.com/|name=Official Canadian website}} {{in lang|fr}}\n* {{IMDb title|1255953|Incendies}}\n* {{AllRovi title|510435|Incendies}}\n* {{Mojo title|incendies|Incendies}}\n* {{Metacritic film|incendies|Incendies}}\n* {{Rotten Tomatoes|incendies|Incendies}}\n\n{{Denis Villeneuve}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Awards for ''Incendies''\n|list =\n{{ACCT Best Picture}}\n{{Lumi\u00e8res Award for Best French-Language Film}}\n{{TFCA Award for Best Canadian Film}}\n{{Prix Iris for Best Film}}\n{{TIFF Best Canadian Film}}\n{{VFCC Award for Best Canadian Film}}\n{{Canadian submission for Academy Awards}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Incendies}}\n[[Category:2010 films]]\n[[Category:2010s war drama films]]\n[[Category:Arabic-language films]]\n[[Category:Best Picture Genie and Canadian Screen Award winners]]\n[[Category:Best French-Language Film Lumi\u00e8res Award winners]]\n[[Category:Canadian mystery films]]\n[[Category:2010s independent films]]\n[[Category:Canadian independent films]]\n[[Category:Canadian war drama films]]\n[[Category:Drama f